folder: Tiffany Pl. & Kane St., Brooklyn, NY
text:
(1)

2-4 Tiffany Place, at the S.W. corner of Kane Street. Also seen is 105-109 Kane Street, north side, between Columbia and Hicks Streets, at the foot of Tiffany Place.

August 5, 1934.

P. L. Sperr.

(2)

The same, showing side of No. 4 Tiffany Place and lot, adjoining the house to the south.

August 5, 1934.

P. L. Sperr.
